rt:model.rt:sub: Sub Calc_But_Color() Dim i As UShort Dim ch_code As UShort For i = 0 To 100 ch_code = PPD_CH(i) & 14 If ((ch_code & 4) > 0) Then Chan_Color(i) = Col_Ar(1) ElseIf ((ch_code & 2) > 0) Then Chan_Color(i) = Col_Ar(3) ElseIf ((ch_code & 14) == 0) Then Chan_Color(i) = Col_Ar(2) Else Chan_Color(i) = Col_Ar(8) End If Next i End Sub
Sub Calc_Sinuses() Dim i As UShort For i = 0 To PPD_CH_num If sin_XQ01(i) == Nothing Then sin_Vars(i) = 0 Else sin_Vars(i) = sin_XQ01(i).Value End If Next i End Sub
rt:model.rt:event: Dim i As UShort Dim DT_name As String For i = 0 To 34 // было 30 If (i < 10) Then DT_name = "2DT0" + CStr(i) + "E01" Else DT_name = "2DT" + CStr(i) + "E01" End If Set sin_XQ01(i) = ANA(DT_name + "_XQ01") sin_Vars(i) = 0 Chan_Color(i) = Col_Ar(8) Next i //PPD_CH_num = количество каналов в основном контуре - 1 (т.к. с 0) + 2 неоперат. контур (межсерв + самодиаг.) If !prim_cluster Then Chan_Color(PPD_CH_num - 1) = Col_Ar(8) Chan_Color(PPD_CH_num) = Col_Ar(8) DT_name = "2DT50E01_XQ01" Set sin_XQ01(PPD_CH_num - 1) = ANA(PPD_CH_num - 1) DT_name = "2DT51E01_XQ01" Set sin_XQ01(PPD_CH_num) = ANA(PPD_CH_num) End If Calc_But_Color()
